            <h2 class="section-title" id="faq-heading" style="margin-top:16px; font-size:1.8rem">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Answers to the questions we hear most often from homeowners planning a construction or remodeling project in Sonoma County.</p>
            <div class="faq-categories" role="tablist">
              <button class="faq-cat-btn active" onclick="filterFAQ('all', this)" role="tab">All Questions</button>
